/ Partial which is used to create dynamic number of ingredients.
/ Ingredients can be deleted or added by clicking on the respective link.
/ Cocoon gem is used to create these dynamic forms.
/ Code adapted from: https://github.com/nathanvda/cocoon
.nested-fields
  .field
    = f.label :description
    = f.text_field :description
  = link_to_remove_association "Remove", f